{{!
    @template mod_scorecard/report_empty_state

    Report empty-state notice. body resolves to either report:empty (no
    attempts at all) or report:empty:filtered (group filter excludes all
    attempts), per the renderer's $filtered argument.

    Context variables required:
    * body  - Lang string report:empty or report:empty:filtered.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "body": "No attempts have been submitted yet."
    }
}}
<div class="scorecard-report-empty alert alert-info">{{{body}}}</div>
